# A simple Evaluator

Reads input from stdin or files, print the results to stdout.
Supports arithmetic and logical operations. Ternary operator is available too.

## Environment

Developed under Ubuntu 12.04 LTS, with GNU Bison 2.5 and flex 2.5.35

# Usage

    $ ./make.sh
    $ ./demo  # interactive mode, reads input from stdin
    $ ./demo test.txt  # reads input from test.txt

Unknown characters and syntax errors will be skipped.

